attributes.title: app format could have been cuter ✨🤢🌺
attributes.review:
i downloaded this app as an alternative to vsco 🌺✨but you would not believe the SOUR DISAPPOINTMENT when i discovered that this app format was not aesthetically pleasing AT ALL😴🤮🥱🤢. i thought i would give it a go for the sake of our orange dictator, and soon after i downloaded it, i was sent an absolutely disgusting red hat (not cute at all)🤢😤😳. as i went to throw the unbefitting hat in the garbage 🗑 🥶it transformed into the fake-haired pervert himself🙀! i cried as he approached me NOT WEARING A MASK😷🤧!! i was trying to teach him social distancing as i backed away when he told me that i was a disgrace to america if i didn’t wear the now cockroach infested MAGA hat 😵🤭😖. as i began to surrender to the cheeto man, the geico gecko (the love of my life💖😍❤️😘) appeared🦎!!! “don’t put the maga hat on, you’ll be brainwashed—“ in that moment the bowler hat guy from Meet the Robinsons appeared with more mind controlling hats🐙 🎩!!!  i watched in horror as he summoned rats that slowly consumed my sugar daddy, who let off screams that were disturbingly human for a lizard🦻🏾💔🦎🐀😓. i quickly escaped to my close friend sofia the first’s house (where i became a princess over night princess👸🏾👑OBVI🙄), while trump and the bowler hat man conspired to consume my indian soul, and promised to avenge my dear reptilian lover. 😭😡🥺💔😘✨🌺💔💖
anyways, the app format could have been a bit more spaced out, maybe use pastel colors instead of the red, white and blue that are currently being used right now? the colors are just a little in your face, and i wouldn’t mind seeing more of a cottagecore vibe to the app instead? well, hope i helped!!💞😘 #justiceforthegeicogecko ☠️😭💔
#trump2020🐀🙀onagravestone🌺✨💞
